WLual4COuMU%3D&h=aa5b1f0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/restore-hong-kongs-autonomy-make-hong-kong-great-again</a>"},{"pid":"a5a6860dae712b3e82fc1c665e2ea56fd546c1ae","tid":1461833,"uid":295218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"好撚肯定傳停飛果班，唔係狗就係弱智<br />\n<br />\n成個下午都唔停<br />\n偏偏收工時間先嚟停，為乜？<br />\n等你班撚樣見做咗成日嘢，攰攰地，就諗住停飛咗所以返屋企抖，然後無人入去<br />\n<br />\n你老闆，尋日係咁，今日又係咁，醒未呀！<br />\n入機場啦<br />\n轉頭過咗收工時間，復飛又無人岀<br />\n然後旅客又怪落班示威者度"},{"pid":"3fe9aca515a768f32f71906dc4f84aac9251282a","tid":1461833,"uid":47801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:43:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7fe4093ee1cb02327a9e59985224862679bad03","tid":1461833,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:43:07.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n但最好隔日咁做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"efde0259707707c3f50c307507563d9a55dd0262","