\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70419b57b6052e2152adecb88af5d5778f877529","tid":1461833,"uid":7760,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"屌你地老母<br />\n下下話鬼 同2014 雨傘有撚分別呀<br />\n依加做乜鳩都話鬼, 咁係咪遲下勇武派玩魔法又屌係鬼呀<br />\n<br />\n又話核彈都唔割, 依加做啲野唔岩心意就屌鬼"},{"pid":"48b35627d41d599a8c8af6b04b7d3c372b91ad65","tid":1461833,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:49:43.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"ed481c530f32f673c3fb69505b06e87f3c7592c2","tid":1461833,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:15.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n但最好隔日咁做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"f9eed1ebf3b33f9a4f5efcc35122cfd1f013f2c1","tid":1461833,"uid":238369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:52:22.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"78e8ef988fff91c7e82101e1eefea9ee3344dc16","tid":1461833,"uid":52574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:53:36.000Z","msg":"你地估接機就真係和理非咁簡單咩......係有藉口掩飾你地衝離境啊！<br />\n「arrival唔夠位 爆左所以我咪去departure靜坐囉」<br />\n明唔明係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人數取勝被動塞</span></span>先係最legit<br />\n而家夾硬阻礙人地出入 只會變左非法禁錮人<br />\n成個行動唔legit 同塞鐵一樣 小貓三四隻塞目的唔太達到又唔legit<br />\n其實琴日癱瘓最大原因從來唔係塞Departure（要知道仲有通道留俾人自由進出），而係交通 + 有機組人員自發罷工<br />\n罷工係基本法賦予嘅權利，但我地限制人地人身自由係變咗剝削人地權利+非法禁錮<br />\n我明大家好想重現琴日癱瘓畫面，但而家人數真係唔夠！！好應該忍下手俾d耐性唔好俾憤怒沖昏頭腦啊！！<br />\n衝左入禁區，一陣有咩事，個單眼女義士都唔安樂！！<br />\n唔好俾情緒主導，癱瘓固然重要 但可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更有智慧地癱而且唔遭人話柄！</span></span><br />\n要接受我地係長期抗爭！其實最應該係煲大某幾日搞大佢配合機組人員罷工（呢個係關鍵），到時你慢慢塞都冇問題！！<br />\n<br />\n我地而家唔係要搞到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「旅客上唔到機」</span></strong></span><br />\n而要係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「班機起唔到飛」</strong></span></span>！"},{"pid":"1e9c6cf162e849e077fcf73ae974e9a653920d17","tid":1461833,"uid":238369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:54:25.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"601cd7e051cee17c19b2c9030446ff1314efd5b3","tid":1461833,"uid":238369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:55:30.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"c20497940c8ae82d0ed241e37dd1268aa57c7620","tid":1461833,"uid":30697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:55:51.000Z","msg":"和理非］<br />\n<br />\n各位 請聽我講 我地唔好直接搬路障阻住旅客check in 或者做破壞<br />\n咁樣只會損壞我地呢次和理非既形象<br />\n我地要醒d等政府自己取消航班<br />\n<br />\n大家抗爭要顧住形象ar!!!<br />\n唔好同旅客爭執 我地要爭取國際認同<br />